data.title: Pedigree Chart 2011 - Kwartierstaat Mike Ridderhof
data.meta_description: Pedigree Chart 2011 - Kwartierstaat Mike Ridderhof - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document is a pedigree chart that traces the ancestry of M.L.H. Ridderhof back several generations. It includes the names of Ridderhof's parents and grandparents, as well as more distant relatives such as great-grandparents and great-great-grandparents. For each individual, it lists their name, birth date and location, death date and location, and spouse's name. The chart traces Ridderhof's ancestry back to the early 1800s and includes over 100 names.
